						               													<description>This is a game in which players break into two teams and face off to complete challenges using the included tiny hands and other included props.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On each round of play, a team makes a wager and takes a turn spinning the spinner to determine their activity. The spinner can land on either Solo, Pairs, or Charades. Additionally the spinner will also determine whether you must use the Tiny Hands props or the Tinier Hands props.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For Solo play, a player is chosen to represent his/her team to complete the activity on the card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For Pairs, two players on a team work together to complete the activity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For Charades, one player on a team must act out as many prompts on the card as he/she can before the timer runs out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Face-Off: If at any time, you draw a card that features the Face-Off symbol, teams must face off and wager their highest points available using either the Tiny or Tinier Hands.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Winning a round: &amp;#10;If your team is successful, you earn the points you wagered.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the other team challenges you, they must wager either the same amount or higher and perform the same challenge. In charade challenges, the opposing team must draw new prompts to complete. If the opposing team is successful, the original team still win points but their wagered token must flip to the black side for a smaller point value.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If either or both teams lose, their wagered token flips to the black side and the token is handed off to the opposing team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Winning the Game:&amp;#10;The first team to reach 31 points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes 2 Tiny Hands, 2 Tinier Hands, 151 Activity Cards, 20 Scoring Tokens, 1 Spinner, 1 String, 1 Ball, 1 Sand Timer, 1 Wager Mat and Instructions&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
